Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:07.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty then! It's finally \Ntime for the last battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like fish, but I can't stand dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, I bet you've got something \Nyou're scared of, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail was challenged to an all-out war \Nwith the strongest Dark Guild, Grimoire Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the fateful battle between Gray and \NUltear, Gray pulled out a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the only enemy left is Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Hades, who has stronger magic power \Nthan any opponent they've ever faced before,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail begins the final battle of \NTenroujima by joining together to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is taking a turn for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning... I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... You're scared of thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's got some cute points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beat Hades!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy! Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the same team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but wouldn't Fried be more suited...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stay here and draw runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the defense to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with Natsu-san and Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can at least support Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pay them back for Gajeel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:30.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here and help Fried with the runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay beside Mira-nee and Elf-niichan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that decides things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect everyone, period!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan! Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've recovered most of my magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hades is probably the only enemy left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks to be the final battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna do our best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed Squad... Move out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Always stay by Natsu's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:17.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Natsu has a trusted friend \Nbeside him, he gets even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:30.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... right... there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Zeref over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the "love" or whatever \Nyou were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zancrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking Zeref, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you and Ultear-san are \Ngonna betray us after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't a member of \NGrimoire Heart any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is Ultear's future...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My... future...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naive fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:38.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:50.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we went to the World of Great Magic, \Nshe'd turn my town back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:59.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... Hikaru and I \Nwere there back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-san promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except that it was Ultear-san \Nwho destroyed the town herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:40.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, man whose name I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have burdened myself \Nonce again with darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... You two seem safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have no intention \Nof doing anything in this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:17.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become no one's \Nally, and no one's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this age is now coming to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I may spring into action once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to destroy \Nme before that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That word he just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep my eyes open...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I keep getting \Nsaved by other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the 7 Kin of Purgatory \Nand Bluenote would be done in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should just admit it, \Nand praise Makarov's troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Me, having to \Nface these foot soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The games played between \Ndemon and fairy are now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now... Shall I play with you a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 3rd generation Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, if you dare, Makarov's brood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} come down {\i1}here{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks he's all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who hurt the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can just teach that guy a lesson, then \Nwe can all leave the island safely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! We'll all get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy... I have a request for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Search around the ship for the source \Nof its power, and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a problem if it \Nstarted to fly again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...for you, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that much to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cast Troia on you just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltrate from the ship's bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a wizard on an even \Nhigher level than our Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go all-out from \Nthe start, at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:40.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him every last bit of power I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to think \Nabout what comes afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to punch this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hades!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taste the power of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's... power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Wing: Moon Gleam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Golden Bull, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tauros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:26.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magically enchant everyone's attack \Npower, defense power, and speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:28.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vernier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Unison Raid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Edge of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People says that their \Nmistakes become "experience".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:52.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But a true mistake does not \Nleave one with any experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:14:01.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For those who make the mistake of facing \Nme, they have no future left at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a scratch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going all out back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The nature of his magic power... has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:19.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that should be \Nenough warm-up exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyed without even a trace left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I will just erase the \Nrest of you one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone, please calm down."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am safe."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Horologium!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:44.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My automatic emergency danger \Navoidance mode has been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:16:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of remember being in a \Nwhole lot of danger myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The danger level was far greater this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you very much, Horologium-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as annoyingly roundabout as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, why are her \Nclothes all that's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an emergency, so only the \Nperson themselves was protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, in there you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kya!"... she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please change into these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're in your debt. \NI give you our thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only protect you this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Horologium!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:49.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Makarov's brood, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be fun after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there no records of me left \Nin the guild's library, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:09.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once the 2nd master of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the name Purehito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:20.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who chose Makarov \Nas the 3rd guildmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we'd believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spouting such crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dance with magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the \Nsound-proofing on this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still hear the thunder loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't hit the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try over here next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick with us, Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I mistake {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Acnologia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Zeref really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:57.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Zeref really said Acnologia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation of Tenroujima \Nis over and done with!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do fairies have tails, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An eternal riddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, an eternal journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, that was the reasoning \Nbehind the name of the guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But your journey will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mavis's will was entrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And my will was entrusted to Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov changed the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with change?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He exposed magic to too much sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:31.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't a living corpse like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We live our lives by putting \Neverything on the line, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the courage to \Nchange, then just stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:42.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down, little devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to blame someone, blame Makarov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:21:01.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Makarov's fault that \Nyou will die suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge... for Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the guy who hurt my old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do fairies have tails, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:23:59.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:00.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:04.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy without a tail is like stir-fried \Nvegetables without any meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the nutty metaphor?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:09.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, if you add meat \Nit turns into a different dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.48,0:24:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's like stir-fried \Nvegetables without the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Man Without the Mark
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we were talking \Nabout fairies, not stir-fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.47,0:24:23.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, let's eat! I'm starving!
